WEBVTT

00:00:59.680 --> 00:01:03.840
I always wanted to play there,
but my mother wouldn’t let me.

00:01:04.280 --> 00:01:06.280
She used to say, “It's dangerous.”

00:01:06.400 --> 00:01:09.040
I did not get the meaning of danger.

00:01:09.220 --> 00:01:13.440
I was always taught to be careful,
never trust anyone.

00:01:13.590 --> 00:01:16.030
A relative even had a problem
with the way I walked.

00:01:16.030 --> 00:01:17.790
“Don’t walk like this, but like this.

00:01:17.860 --> 00:01:21.570
If you walk properly, your chest will 
stand out and men will find it strange.”

00:01:22.350 --> 00:01:24.640
One day, I understood everything.

00:01:24.840 --> 00:01:27.480
I was 13, when on my way back from school,

00:01:27.480 --> 00:01:30.830
on the road, a man suddenly touched me.